{"tid":1500671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★瘋搶！映日灣次輪銷售216伙　中原 ：料單日可沽清","createTime":"2019-08-24T05:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:36:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e69d40f267e87c5f15c2108ab04b691afea432b6","tid":1500671,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"他指，日出康城項目日前公布首張價單，市場認購反應熱烈，雖然客源或與映日灣重疊，但由於剛性需求強烈，相信兩盤可吸納居屋後籌客源，加上負利率年代，物業仍是港人主要儲蓄工具，兩盤銷售反應將同樣熱烈。昨日美股雖跌600多點，而且美國再宣佈向中國加徵關稅，但以今日一手盤銷售情況看來，本港置業氣氛與中美貿易戰關係不大。陳永傑表示，如果日出康城項目可趕於本月推出，調整本月一手預測至1,500宗，與上月相若。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3197645/org/9672060b4eb14bccce16d3621f35b6b2.jpg/pauVaSV0hw1gFZOAubUBcKLrBXG1uK5IDK3LJwytyyc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3197645%2Forg%2F9672060b4eb14bccce16d3621f35b6b2.jpg%2FpauVaSV0hw1gFZOAubUBcKLrBXG1uK5IDK3LJwytyyc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=16deeef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/367465/%E6%98%A0%E6%97%A5%E7%81%A3%E6%AC%A1%E8%BC%AA%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE216%E4%BC%99-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E9%99%B3%E6%B0%B8%E5%82%91%E6%96%99%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%AF%E6%B2%BD%E6%B8%85-%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%AE%A2%E4%BD%946%E6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F367465%2F%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%2594%25AE216%25E4%25BC%2599-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25BD%25946%25E6%2588%2590&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=1b673b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/367465/%E6%98%A0%E6%97%A5%E7%81